name: SNOW MONKEY SHROOM
description: Combining my doodle style with the Ai image generator snowpixel.app @snowpixelapp (TWITTER) which creates an image using the series of words I give it in a sentence construct. Then I overlay with my doodles. I really recommend trying it out and helpful hint, make the sentence really surreal. Think Alice In Wonderland. The title of this piece was not the original string of words.
